Text:
So far I've seen girl no 1, 2 & 3 and I must say...
No 1 & 2 -primo, very realistic first-timers also hot girls (no 2 has bad teeth, soon they all fall out and she's totally harmless). No 3 is what I need to open my mind about, she's a fucking ogre. 

...well so far 2/3, it's easy to skip past Mrs. Shrek.
